title: 2 hours downloading???
body: anyone suffering the same thing? 677Mb update, and only 80 KBPS, r u kiding me??? im using NBN and no one els using the internet, i need to wait 140 mins,lmao, wtf is that update??? whats in there?

replies.body:
NBN with speed booster, was done practically instantly.
